00:42:26,680 --> 00:42:29,325
Hey, seriously, man.
You're not supposed to be here.

604
00:42:30,040 --> 00:42:33,496
I'm performing a delivery.
You are?

605
00:42:34,020 --> 00:42:36,190
Patient whose prenatal care
I've been handling.

606
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:37,880
I just took her on
a couple of minutes ago.

607
00:42:38,640 --> 00:42:40,961
Of course, I'll need one
of you two guys to supervise.

608
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:44,131
When's she due? Late March.

609
00:42:45,750 --> 00:42:47,176
That's five months from now.

610
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:51,510
Thank God these chairs
are comfortable.

